### Mon profil
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Modifier mon profil
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

